high_descs: Turn right, then head towards the desk.
Open the left door in the desk.
Pick up the brass candy dish inside then close the door.
Turn left then turn on the lamp against the wall.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a brass candy dish and turn on a lamp.

high_descs: Walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk over to the wooden dresser.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the dresser and take out the golden vase, then close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the tall lamp to the left of the dresser.
Turn on the light of the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a golden vase in the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Move to the bottom left side of the cabinet
Pick up the gold vase in the cabinet
Carry the gold vase to the floor lamp on the right
anns.task_desc: Carry a vase while turning on a lamp
